Author:		Ian-Woo Kim
Maintainer: 	Ian-Woo Kim <ianwookim@gmail.com>
Build-Type: 	Simple
Cabal-Version:  >= 1.8
Data-files: template/HROOT.cabal.st
            -- template/TypeCast.hs
            -- template/*.h.st
            -- template/*.hs.st
            -- template/*.hsc.st
            -- template/*.cpp.st

Executable HROOT-generate
